article.description: — Shaquille Walters had a career-high 21 points as Northeastern topped Duquesne 71-55 in the U.S. Virgin Islands Paradise Jam on Friday night.
article.headline: Walters scores 21 to carry Northeastern over Duquesne 71-55
article.linkText: Walters scores 21 to carry Northeastern over Duquesne 71-55
article.story: ST. THOMAS, U.S. Virgin Islands -- — Shaquille Walters had a career-high 21 points as Northeastern topped Duquesne 71-55 in the U.S. Virgin Islands Paradise Jam on Friday night. Vito Cubrilo had 11 points for Northeastern (2-2). Chris Doherty added 10 points. Nikola Djogo had eight rebounds. Amir Spears had 15 points for the Dukes (1-3). Tre Williams added 11 points and 11 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
